PC PC_TicketMachine@TicketMachine
atom coin
process TicketMachine@coin
operator OpAfterCoin.Choice
after coin->OpAfterCoin
op_connector OpAfterCoin->TicketMachine
atom red
atom green
op_connector OpAfterCoin->red
op_connector OpAfterCoin->green
atom ejectCoins
process ReturnCoins@ejectCoins
after red->ReturnCoins
operator OpAfterGreen.IntChoice
after green->OpAfterGreen
op_connector OpAfterGreen->ReturnCoins
atom issueTicket
op_connector OpAfterGreen->issueTicket
